  "description": "<a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518128/\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/daeec2c4fd92470393c9471f0d561a42.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tCarl Rinsch, in his feature film debut, directed the adventure-fantasy that stars Keanu Reeves as Kai, a half Japanese, half- British samurai that joins a group of outcast samurai to seek <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vengeance\" target=\"_blank\">vengeance</a> upon a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/treacherous\" target=\"_blank\">treacherous</a> overlord who killed their master. The film is a fictionalized account of the true forty-seven Ronin tale, but will feature fantastical elements including <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sorcery\" target=\"_blank\">sorcery</a> and witches.《浪人47》是卡尔&middot;里辛的电影处女作，这部由基努&middot;李维斯主演的魔幻冒险片讲述了日英混血的武士卡伊（基努&middot;李维斯饰演）加入了无家可归的武士组织，为他们死去的主人复仇的故事。这部电影根据日本历史的真人真事改编，还加入了一些包括巫术和巫师在内的奇幻因素。</p>\n<p>\n\t47 Ronin is set to be released on Christmas Day 2013 after being bumped twice previously by Universal.《浪人47》由美国环球影片公司投资拍摄，将于今年圣诞节上映。</p>\n<p>\n\tHiroyuki Sanada (The Wolverine), Kou Shibasaki, Tadanobu Asano (Thor) andRinko Kikuchi (Pacific Rim) also star in the pic.真田广之（出演《金刚狼》）、柴崎幸、浅野忠信（出演《雷神》）和菊地凛子（出演《环太平洋》）也都有出演。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/78aac68ff82f4c45852219d15843fb20.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/d32ac45283d146f6aae0cfb9f2ea8d6f.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/3eae5bb19cfc4f0c819411100b43c0a2.jpg\" /></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518128/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518128\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"bord